name: cleanreg
description: Contains a small python script to clean up a docker registry (v2).
full_description:
# Registry Cleaner

This is a small tool to delete tags, or, to be more correct, delete image manifests, from a Docker Registry implementing the API v2.

For the code, usage details and issues please go to the [Cleanreg GitHub Repository](https://github.com/hcguersoy/cleanreg).
